    {
      "id": "person:speaker-01",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Rina"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:067e023884661dc8",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 181,
        "char_start": 6,
        "episode_id": "a283fe88-fdec-51b4-8014-431b4a7ce670",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Welcome back to Below the Surface. Today we're talking about wreck diving, and I'm joined by Marco, technical diver and underwater archaeologist. Marco, thanks for being here.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 6000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 0,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "person:speaker-02",
      "properties": {
        "name": "Marco"
      },
      "type": "Person"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:585882210026efa4",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 296,
        "char_start": 189,
        "episode_id": "a283fe88-fdec-51b4-8014-431b4a7ce670",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Thanks, Rina. Excited for this one \u2014 wreck-diving fundamentals is something I've been thinking about a lot.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 12000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 6000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:52ad4a4d9df1f8c9",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 507,
        "char_start": 303,
        "episode_id": "a283fe88-fdec-51b4-8014-431b4a7ce670",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "Before we dive in, a quick word from our sponsor Suunto. Suunto builds dive computers and outdoor watches that you trust because they don't quit when conditions change. Use code POD for an extended trial.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 18000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 12000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:78c929f34f35848e",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 593,
        "char_start": 507,
        "episode_id": "a283fe88-fdec-51b4-8014-431b4a7ce670",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "What does that look like day-to-day? What's the most underrated piece of wreck diving?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 24000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 18000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:4535fb3d04a57b77",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 821,
        "char_start": 601,
        "episode_id": "a283fe88-fdec-51b4-8014-431b4a7ce670",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-02",
        "text": "Yeah, so \u2014 Wreck penetration is a planning problem first, a buoyancy problem second. The dive happens at the desk. We've seen this play out at teams using Suunto. And the second-order effect is the part most people miss.",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 30000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 24000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:880f12ce9fac3a35",
      "properties": {
        "char_end": 930,
        "char_start": 828,
        "episode_id": "a283fe88-fdec-51b4-8014-431b4a7ce670",
        "speaker_id": "person:speaker-01",
        "text": "What does the failure mode look like? What's the structural angle most listeners don't have access to?",
        "timestamp_end_ms": 36000,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 30000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/p03_e01.txt"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    }
